 almost no serifs/terminations to the strokes, excpt for the slight extension of the apex of alpha and delta. Alpha has broken bar; omicron is slightly ovoid and full size; pi has equal length verticals; epsilon is lunate; phi is rhomboid.",[37,43,47,51],{"type":38,"l":39,"from":40,"to":40,"h":41,"unit":42},"letterHeight","Line 1","line1","12","mm",{"type":38,"l":44,"from":45,"to":45,"h":46,"unit":42},"Line 2","line2","12-14",{"type":48,"l":49,"from":40,"to":45,"h":50,"unit":42},"interlinear","Interlineation line 1 to 2","2",{"type":48,"l":52,"from":45,"to":53,"h":54,"unit":42},"Interlineation line 2 to 3","line3","1-2",{"_":56,"notBefore":57,"notAfter":58,"evidence":59,"precision":60},"4th century CE",301,400,"lettering","low",[62,66],{"_":63,"type":64,"ref":65},"Megara Hyblaea","ancient","http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462307",{"_":67,"type":68,"ref":69},"Megara Iblea","modern","http://sws.geonames.org/8063661",[71],[72,73],37.2038,15.18274,[],"Italy","Sicily",{"_":78,"role":79,"ref":80},"Antiquarium di Megara Hyblaia","museum","http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/104",{"_":82,"mainLang":83,"languages":84},"Ancient Greek","grc",[82],{"n":86,"url":87,"height":88,"width":89,"desc":90,"surfaceType":91},"screen","ISic004390_tiled.tif","3680px","5520px","I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana","front",[],[94,95],"Tréziny, 2011, À propos d’une inscription funéraire paléochrétienne de Mégara Hyblaea","Tréziny, 2018, Mégara Hyblaea. 7, La ville classique, hellénistique et romaine",[97,98],"DFXDQ8GT","5UHWUE4K",[100,101,102,15,19,103,104,105,106,107,104,108,109,83],"isic004390","fragmentary early christian funerary inscription",{"_":12},"marble","megara hyblaea","megara iblea","italy","sicily","antiquarium di megara hyblaia","ancient greek","\u003Cspan class=\"textpartnumber\" id=\"aba\">fragment (physical) a\u003C/span>  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpar